{"sn1.71:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.71 ","sn1.71:0.2":"8. Chetvavagga ","sn1.71:0.3":"Chetvasutta ","sn1.71:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn1.71:1.2":"Ekamantam thita kho sa devata bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn1.71:2.1":"“Kimsu chetva sukham seti, ","sn1.71:2.2":"kimsu chetva na socati; ","sn1.71:2.3":"Kissassu ekadhammassa, ","sn1.71:2.4":"vadham rocesi gotama”ti. ","sn1.71:3.1":"“Kodham chetva sukham seti, ","sn1.71:3.2":"kodham chetva na socati; ","sn1.71:3.3":"Kodhassa visamulassa, ","sn1.71:3.4":"madhuraggassa devate; ","sn1.71:3.5":"Vadham ariya pasamsanti, ","sn1.71:3.6":"tanhi chetva na socati”ti. "}